  string
  line 1
  line `THE ACQUISITION OF CERTAIN AREA AT AYODHYA ACT, 1993`
  line _____________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ___________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `A CQUISITION OF THE AREA IN AYODHYA`
  line `3. Acquisition of rights in respect of certain area.`
  line `4. General effect of vesting.`
  line `5. Duty of person or State Government in charge of the management of the area to deliver all assets,`
  line etc.
  line `6. Power of Central Government to direct vesting of the area in another authority or body or trust.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `M ANAGEMENT AND ADMINISTRATION OF PROPERTY`
  line `7. Management of property by Government.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `M ISCELLANEOUS`
  line `8. Payment of amount.`
  line `9. Act to override all other enactments.`
  line `10. Penalties.`
  line `11. Protection of action taken in good faith.`
  line `12. Power to make rules.`
  line `13. Repeal and saving.`
  line `THE SCHEDULE.`
